@node "Roger" "Roger HÍgensen"


      Roger HÍgensen
      MSI Software
      msi@sn.no
      http://www.sn.no/~msi/index.htm

      He is the author of DVC.

      Roger, thanks for the ability to distribute it with DTypeGuide.
      Dear reader of this guide, So you are be able to check your
      datatypes easily.

      Please respect the hard work of Roger and download the complete
      DVC archiv from Aminet - util/misc/DVC.lha
      DVC 2.2 can handle device/-Handler files also, like those in
      DEVS: and L: and also Libraries etc.
      Here you can get some @{"information" link "dvc.readme/main"}.

@endnode
